<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>duō qí dǎo duō gē shēng 迦南902</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 duō qí dǎo duō gē shēng, shén de ér nǚ dōu dāng rú cǐ xíng.
 duō xún qiú duō dú jīng, hēi yè shēn shēn xīn zhōng yě guāng míng.
 zhǔ a wǒ men děng hòu nǐ, nǐ bù huì wàng jì nǐ míng xià de bǎi xìng.
 suī yǒu chóu xì zhòu yè gōng jī, gèng yào kào nǐ yīn qín qù zuò gōng.
 fèng zhǔ de míng bǎ fú yīn jiǎng, yī bìng gǎn guǐ xíng yì néng.
 shí shí tí xǐng bù yào pà, jiān dìng gēn suí yé sū zǒu líng chéng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>902</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>